Package language.grammarElements

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AST  
    Canvas
    Class which represents the drawing element according to the given parameters (width and height)
    Param
    Class which represents a parameter (given by the user) for the AST
    Params
    Class which represents a list of parameters (given by the user) for the AST
    Shape
    Class which handles the given shapes given by the user (circle, ellipse, etc.) and add them in the drawing to be shown to the user
    Sheet
    Class to draw the shapes previously added to the drawing
